{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-article-tsx","path":"/arduino-programming/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1>Arduino Programming</h1>\n<p>Code for Arduino is typically written in <a href=\"../cpp/\">C++</a> in the <a href=\"https://www.arduino.cc/en/software\">Arduino IDE</a> or <a href=\"https://create.arduino.cc/editor\">Arduino Web Editor</a>.</p>\n<p>The web editor is preferred over the IDE because it is always current and makes code sharing easier. To enable communication from the browser to a local Arduino device requires <a href=\"https://create.arduino.cc/getting-started/plugin\">installation of the Arduino Create Plugin</a>.</p>\n<h2>Enable Serial Logging</h2>\n<p>Serial logging is useful for debugging. To start serial logging, call the <a href=\"https://www.arduino.cc/reference/en/language/functions/communication/serial/begin/\"><code class=\"language-text\">Serial.begin()</code> function</a> in the <code class=\"language-text\">setup</code> function:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cpp\"><pre class=\"language-cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">setup</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  Serial<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">begin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">9600</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.arduino.cc/reference/en/language/functions/communication/serial/println/\"><code class=\"language-text\">Serial.println()</code> function</a> can then print values to the serial monitor.</p>","fields":{"slug":"/arduino-programming/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Arduino Programming","tags":["arduino","cpp"]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/arduino-programming/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2270328656","3794076007","80858887"]}